title: Fantasia of the Wind
description: IntroductionFantasia of the Wind is is an adventure puzzle role-playing game (AVG + RPG) produced by Fantasia Group, which is the first game of the Fantasia Series. The engine is RPGMaker MV, supporting controllers, mouse and keyboard operations.It is an adventure story about a girl named Sandra who lived in a small village.
